### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@userId = 
@nickname = 

### Crear un nuevo usuario con contraseña hasheada
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Diego Requena",
  "nickname": "diebozzz",
  "email": "diegomnk@hotmail.com",
  "password": "drequena123",
  "bio": "Apasionado del fitness y la tecnología"
}

### Login de usuario (NUEVO)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "diegomnk@hotmail.com",
  "password": "contrasenia123"
}

### Cambiar contraseña (ahora con hash)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{userId}}/password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "contrasenia123",
  "newPassword": "nuevaContrasenia456"
}

### Buscar usuarios por nickname o nombre
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/search/diego

### Obtener perfil público por nickname
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/profile/{{nickname}}

### Obtener todos los usuarios
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users

### Actualizar perfil (incluyendo nickname)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nickname": "nuevo_nickname",
  "bio": "Nueva biografía",
  "profile_picture": "https://example.com/photo.jpg"
}

### Obtener un usuario específico
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{userId}}

### Cambiar contraseña de un usuario
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{userId}}/password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "password123",
  "newPassword": "newPassword456"
}

### Seguir a un usuario
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{userId}}/follow
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "follower_id": "USER_ID_DEL_SEGUIDOR"
}

### Dejar de seguir a un usuario
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{userId}}/unfollow
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "follower_id": "USER_ID_DEL_SEGUIDOR"
}

### Eliminar un usuario
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{userId}}

